text: American League Park may refer to: ==United States== ===Baseball parks=== *American League Park (Baltimore), renamed Oriole Park *American League Park, the first of two former baseball parks in Washington, DC with that name, the second ("American League Park II") often known as Boundary Field *American League Park (New York City), commonly known as Hilltop Park ==See also== *League Park (disambiguation) *National League Park (disambiguation)
title: American League Park (disambiguation)
